---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
---
<link rel="canonical" href="https://cayadservices.com/terms-of-service/" />
<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/terms.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Cayad Auto Transport"
content="Terms of Service for Cayad Auto Transport - Read our terms and conditions for using our website and WhatsApp Business API services.">
  <container
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <h1
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
        data-aos="fade-down"
      >
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
    </div>
  </container>

  <container
    class="w-[80%] xs:w-full xs:px-4 sm:w-full sm:px-4 flex flex-col mb-8 items-center mx-auto"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">
      Cayad Services LLC Terms of Service
    </h1>

    <p class="text-[#555] mt-8">
      Thanks for using Cayad Services LLC's website. These following terms and conditions of use ("TOU") apply to your use of our website and the content contained therein ("Site"). The following TOU and our <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="text-btn-blue underline">Privacy Policy</a> define your use of our website, and related products and services. By using this Site, you accept these TOU so please review them carefully. If you are an employee or agent of an organization, by using our Site and/or services, you agree to the TOU on behalf of your organization. The terms "you", "your" and "yours" mean you, the user. The terms "we", "us", "our", "ours", and "Cayad" mean Cayad Services LLC.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-4 mt-8 w-full">
      <p class="text-red-700 font-bold">BINDING ARBITRATION</p>
      <p class="text-red-600 mt-2">THESE TOU CONTAIN PROVISIONS THAT GOVERN HOW CLAIMS YOU AND CAYAD MAY HAVE AGAINST EACH OTHER CAN BE BROUGHT. THESE PROVISIONS WILL, WITH LIMITED EXCEPTION, REQUIRE YOU TO SUBMIT CLAIMS YOU HAVE AGAINST CAYAD TO BINDING AND FINAL ARBITRATION ON AN INDIVIDUAL BASIS, NOT AS A PLAINTIFF OR CLASS MEMBER IN ANY CLASS, GROUP OR REPRESENTATIVE ACTION OR PROCEEDING. PLEASE REVIEW SECTION ON ARBITRATION FOR THE DETAILS REGARDING YOUR AGREEMENT TO ARBITRATE ANY DISPUTES WITH CAYAD.</p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">1. TOU Modifications</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      These TOU may be modified at any time by us upon posting of the modified TOU. Any such modifications shall be effective immediately. You can view the most recent version of these TOU at this page. Cayad may terminate these TOU at any time, with or without notice, for any reason. Each use of the Site by you shall constitute and be deemed your unconditional acceptance of these TOU. If you do not agree to these TOU, do not use the Site.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">2. Services</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      Services includes, but is not limited to, the Site, related technologies, our WhatsApp Business API integration, and any software, data, reports, text, images, sounds, video, and content made available through any of the foregoing, and any new features added to or augmenting the Services, and all enhancements, modifications, and derivative works thereof ("Services").
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">3. Privacy</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      Your visit to our Site is also governed by our <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="text-btn-blue underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">4. Ownership</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      All content included on this Site is, and shall continue to be, the property of Cayad or its content suppliers and is protected under applicable copyright, patent, trademark, and other proprietary rights. Any copying, redistribution, use or publication by you of any such content or any part of the Site is prohibited, except as authorized or approved in writing by us.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">5. Minors</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      This Site is not directed towards children. If you are a minor (under the age of 18), please do not submit any personal information to this Site. <strong>IF YOU ARE YOUNGER THAN 18 YEARS OLD, PLEASE DO NOT USE THIS SITE OR ANY OF ITS SERVICES FOR ANY PURPOSE AT ANY TIME.</strong>
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">6. Site Use</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      Cayad grants you a limited, revocable, non-exclusive license to use this Site solely for your own personal use and not for republication, distribution, assignment, sublicense, sale, preparation of derivative works, or other use. The Site and any part of it may not be reproduced, copied, framed or otherwise exploited for any commercial purpose without the express prior written consent of Cayad.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">7. Use Restrictions</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      You will access and use the Service for lawful and authorized purposes only. You may not:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8">
      <li>Exceed the scope of your authorized use of the Service</li>
      <li>Access the Service by any means other than through the interface provided by us</li>
      <li>Introduce any viruses, Trojan horses, worms, logic bombs or other malicious material</li>
      <li>Use any robot, spider or other automatic device to access the Site</li>
      <li>Attempt to probe, scan or test the vulnerability of our systems</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">8. WhatsApp Business API Specific Terms</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      When using our WhatsApp Business API integration, you additionally agree to:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8">
      <li>Comply with WhatsApp's Business Policy and Meta's Terms of Service</li>
      <li>Not send spam, misleading, or fraudulent messages through our service</li>
      <li>Obtain proper consent from your customers before sending them messages</li>
      <li>Not use our WhatsApp integration for any illegal activities</li>
      <li>Respect the 24-hour customer service window for free-form messaging</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">9. Third Party Services</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      The Service may enable linkage between various online third-party services such as third party websites, email, cloud storage, social, and similar services ("Third-Party Services"). Your use of Third-Party Services is governed solely by the agreement between you and the provider of such Third-Party Service, and Cayad is not liable for any loss or claim that you may have against any such third party.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">10. Indemnification</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      You agree to indemnify, defend and hold Cayad and our partners, affiliates and our and their employees, officers, directors harmless from and against any and all liabilities arising from your violation of these TOU or use of the Services.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">11. Disclaimer</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      WE DO NOT WARRANT THAT ACCESS TO OR USE OF THE SITE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED OR ERROR-FREE. THE SERVICES AND INFORMATION ON THE SITE IS PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS," "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS. CAYAD DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO ANY IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">12. Limitation of Liability</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES WILL CAYAD BE LIABLE OR RESPONSIBLE FOR ANY DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, SPECIAL, EXEMPLARY, PUNITIVE, OR OTHER DAMAGES ARISING OUT OF OR IN ANY WAY RELATING TO THE SITE, YOUR SITE USE, OR THE CONTENT, EVEN IF ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">13. Arbitration</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      Any dispute, controversy, or claim between us arising out of or relating in any way to these TOU, and/or any of Cayad's offerings, Services, Site, content or software will be resolved by binding arbitration, rather than in court. The arbitration will be conducted by the National Arbitration Mediation ("NAM") under its rules. The arbitration will take place in St. Petersburg, Florida.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">14. Class Action Waiver</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      We each agree that any dispute resolution proceedings or lawsuits, whether in arbitration or in a court of law, will be conducted only on an individual basis and not in a class or representative action.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">15. Applicable Law</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2">
      You agree that the laws of the State of Illinois, without regard to conflicts of laws provisions will govern these TOU and any dispute that may arise between you and Cayad or its affiliates.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full">16. Contact Information</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 w-full">
      If you have any questions, comments or notices regarding these TOU, please contact us at:
    </p>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-4 w-full">
      <strong>Cayad Services LLC</strong><br />
      7901 4th St N<br />
      St. Petersburg, FL 33702<br />
      Email: info@cayadservices.com<br />
      Phone: (469) 619-0747
    </p>

    
  </container>

  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
</Layout>